Here will be the introduction to `Stata`. Now an example of code visualization:


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(Statamarkdown)
```

::: {.cell}

```{.stata .cell-code}
clear all
set obs 10000
gen x = -3 + 6/(_N-1)*(_n - 1)
gen y = normalden(x)
line y x
```

